    <p>An ex­per­i­men­tal vir­tual bus lane is likely to be im­ple­mented for Lorong Ah Soo (to­wards Hougang Av­enue 3). The two-lane road has no space for a phys­i­cal bus lane, so this smart sig­nalling sys­tem tells mo­torists to move to the right lane to make way for ap­proach­ing buses.</p>

